<h2>Why Travel Sleep Sucks (And How This Kit Fixes It)</h2>
<p>Hotels and flights introduce three sleep saboteurs: ambient noise you can't control, light from hallways and windows, and dry cabin air that wrecks your breathing and throat. Most travelers power through with earbuds and a cheap mask. This kit solves all three with portable, TSA-friendly gear that actually works.</p>
