<h2>What's Inside the Travel Sleep Kit</h2>
<p>This is a curated bundle of three proven products optimized for travel. The Restnature White Noise Machine is genuinely pocket-sized (1.8" x 1.8") and weighs less than a phone—it charges via USB-C and runs 6-8 hours per charge. The Bluetooth Sleep Mask offers full blackout with flat embedded speakers that don't dig in when you sleep. The Breazy Mouth Tape is a 30-pack of medical-grade adhesive strips. Together, they weigh under half a pound and fit in a single carry-on pocket. You save $24 by buying them as a bundle instead of separately.</p>

